face%20their%20final%20fate%20at%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20soon.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETwo%20Illinois-based%20educational%20toy%20companies%20filed%20an%20emergency%20request%20Tuesday%20asking%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20to%20take%20up%20their%20case%20as%20soon%20as%20possible%2C%20rather%20than%20letting%20it%20continue%20to%20play%20out%20in%20lower%20courts%20since%20%26quot%3Bit%20will%20inevitably%20fall%20to%20this%20Court%20to%20resolve%20it%20definitively.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EToy%20companies%20Learning%20Resources%20and%20hand2mind%20filed%20an%20initial%20suit%20on%20April%2022%2C%20challenging%20Trump's%20use%20of%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhat-may-happen-next-court-strikes-down-trumps-ieepa-tariffs-2025-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EInternational%20Emergency%20Economic%20Powers%20Act%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20impose%20tariffs%20without%20going%20through%20Congress.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFor%20months%2C%20we've%20had%20dozens%20of%20people%20working%20full-time%20or%20part-time%20on%20addressing%20all%20aspects%20of%20the%20tariffs%20%E2%80%94%20you%20can%20hardly%20imagine%20anything%20more%20disruptive%2C%26quot%3B%20Rick%20Woldenberg%2C%20CEO%20of%20Learning%20Resources%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider.%20%26quot%3BThis%20is%20an%20emergency%2C%20and%20so%20time%20is%20of%20the%20essence.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20IEEPA%20tariffs%20have%20thus%20far%20been%20ruled%20unlawful%20by%20both%20the%20US%20District%20Court%20in%20the%20District%20of%20Columbia%20and%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdonald-trump-tariffs-blocked-federal-court-2025-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ECourt%20of%20International%20Trade%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20different%20grounds%20in%20separate%20lawsuits%2C%20including%20Woldenberg's%20case%20filed%20in%20Washington%2C%20DC.%20But%20in%20both%20instances%2C%20the%20Court%20of%20Appeals%20has%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffederal-appeals-court-has-temporarily-reinstated-trumps-tariffs-business-lawsuit-2025-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Estayed%20the%20injunction%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20the%20tariffs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20light%20of%20the%20tariffs'%20massive%20impact%20on%20virtually%20every%20business%20and%20consumer%20across%20the%20Nation%2C%20and%20the%20unremitting%20whiplash%20caused%20by%20the%20unfettered%20tariffing%20power%20the%20President%20claims%2C%20challenges%20to%20the%20IEEPA%20tariffs%20cannot%20await%20the%20normal%20appellate%20process%2C%26quot%3B%20wrote%20Pratik%20A.%20Shah%2C%20the%20lawyer%20for%20the%20case%2C%20in%20the%20petition%20to%20the%20Supreme%20Court.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELearning%20Resources%20and%20hand2mind%20are%20not%20the%20only%20businesses%20to%20have%20sued%20over%20Trump's%20tariffs.%20At%20least%20two%20similar%20lawsuits%2C%20one%20from%20a%20small%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsmall-women-owned-business-florida-lawsuit-sues-trump-china-tariffs-2025-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ewomen-owned%20business%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20Florida%20and%20the%20other%20from%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmain-street-trump-trade-war-tariffs-small-businesses-impact-2025-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Efive%20owner-run%20businesses%3C%2Fa%3E%20across%20various%20states%2C%20are%20facing%20similar%20court%20proceedings.%20Neither%20has%20thus%20far%20appealed%20to%20the%20Supreme%20Court%2C%20as%20their%20cases%20are%20also%20stayed%20by%20federal%20appeals%20courts.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20lawsuits%20share%20the%20common%20argument%20that%20Trump%20has%20overstepped%20his%20authority%20by%20imposing%20tariffs%20under%20IEEPA%2C%20a%20law%20they%20said%20does%20not%20give%20the%20president%20unilateral%20power%20to%20impose%20trade%20duties.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20toy%20companies%20are%20specifically%20suing%20over%20Trump's%2010%25%20baseline%20tariff%20on%20most%20imports%20and%20an%20additional%202