nto%20the%20force%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20wrote%20in%20an%20email%20to%20BI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221356%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Detachment%20201's%20commissioning%20ceremony%20in%20Conmy%20Hall%2C%20Joint%20Base%20Myer-Henderson%20Hall%2C%20Va.%2C%20June%2013%2C%202025%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6851d69785e81483682c4a69%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22904%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ESecretary%20of%20the%20Army%20Dan%20Driscoll%20and%20Army%20Chief%20of%20Staff%20General%20Randy%20George%20attended%20the%20Detachment%20201%20commissioning%20ceremony%20in%20Conmy%20Hall%2C%20Joint%20Base%20Myer-Henderson%20Hall%2C%20Virginia%2C%20June%2013%2C%202025.%3Cp%3ELeroy%20Council%2FUS%20Army%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWilliam%20Atterbury%2C%20the%20president%20of%20the%20American%20Railway%20Association%2C%20received%20a%20direct%20commission%20into%20the%20Army%20in%201917%20and%20served%20as%20the%20director-general%20of%20transportation%20for%20Allied%20Expeditionary%20Forces%20in%20France.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOther%20notable%20examples%20include%20the%20president%20of%20the%20Columbia%20Gas%20and%20Electric%20Corporation%20of%20New%20York%2C%20Edward%20Reynolds%2C%20who%20commissioned%20as%20an%20Army%20colonel%20to%20serve%20as%20chief%20of%20the%20Medical%20Supply%20Service%20during%20World%20War%20II%2C%20and%20General%20Motors%20leader%2C%20William%20Knudsen%2C%20who%20direct%20commissioned%20as%20a%20lieutenant%20general%20and%20became%20the%20director%20of%20production%20for%20the%20War%20Department.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20new%20tech%20lieutenant%20colonels%20will%20have%20to%20adhere%20to%20Army%20standards%2C%20Butler%20said%2C%20and%20will%20be%20expected%20to%20perform%20the%20service's%20annual%20fitness%20test%20to%20stay%20in%20good%20standing.%20They%20will%20spend%20around%20two%20weeks%20per%20year%20working%2C%20roughly%20the%20minimum%20required%20for%20military%20reservis