n%20is%20that%20%26quot%3Bthe%20F-35I%20has%20been%20a%20critical%20and%20highly%20successful%20leading%20edge%20capability%20in%20the%20overall%20Israeli%20air%20campaign%20at%20every%20stage.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221600%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22An%20F-35I%20Israeli%20fighter%20jet%20used%20in%20strikes%20against%20Iran.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F684c2fb4f748d8c055f3a565%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221066%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20operation%20is%20showcasing%20the%20strengths%20of%20the%20F-35%20specifically%20in%20fulfilling%20various%20roles%20in%20air%20campaigns.%3Cp%3EIsrael%20Defense%20Forces%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20jet's%20involvement%20isn't%20necessarily%20surprising%20as%20penetrating%20contested%20airspace%20and%20suppressing%20enemy%20defenses%20is%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fus-fighter-jets-israel-air-war-gaza-2024-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ewhat%20the%20F-35%20is%20designed%20to%20do%20and%20what%20Israel%20bought%20it%20for%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20he%20said.%20That%20said%2C%20this%20moment%20is%20an%20opportunity%20to%20showcase%20the%20jet's%20prowess.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20jet%2C%20Bronk%20said%2C%20%26quot%3Boffers%20a%20combination%20of%20stealth%2C%20capability%20to%20rapidly%20detect%2C%20identify%2C%20and%20geolocate%20radar-emitting%20threats%20like%20air%20defense%20systems%2C%20pass%20those%20targets%20to%20other%20aircraft%20or%20strike%20them%20itself%2C%20and%20conduct%20electronic%20warfare%20attacks%20to%20suppress%20said%20targets%20to%20protect%20other%20aircraft%20and%20get%20weapons%20through%20to%20targets.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20F-35%20Joint%20Strike%20Fighter%20is%20a%20single-engine%2C%20multi-role%20stealth%20aircraft%20made%20by%20US%20defense%20contractor%20Lockheed%20Martin%20and%20employed%20by%20countries%20around%20the%20world.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20US%20military%20operates%20three%20variants%20of%20the%20jet%2C%20the%20A%20for%20conventional%20take-off%2C%20the%20B%20for%20short%20take-off%20and%20vertical%20landing%2C%20and%20the%20C%20for%20carrier%20operations.%20Most%20allied%20and%20partner%20nations%20operate%20one%20of%20the%20three%20variants%2C%20but%20Israel%20flies%20a%20unique%20F-35%20variant.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fisrael-war-planes-fighter-jets-f35-2024-4%23on-thursday-the-israeli-air-force-launched-over-200-fighter-jets-including-f-35-i-planes-in-a-preemptive-strike-targeting-irans-nuclear-program-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EIsrael's%20F-35I%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20its%20only%20fifth-generation%20aircraft.%20It%20was%20the%20first%20military%20to%20use%20the%20F-35%20in%20combat%20in%202018.%20It%20currently%20operates%20just%20under%2040%20of%20them%20but%20is%20acquiring%20more.%20Israel's%20specific%20model%20is%20a%20subvariant%20of%20the%20F-35A%20the%20US%20Air%20Force%20flies.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhat%20makes%20the%20F-35I%20%26quot%3BAdir%26quot%3B%20unique%20is%20that%20Israel%20can%20modify%20the%20mission%20data%20and%20programming%20of%20the%20jets%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Eand%20integrate%20domestically%20developed%20systems%2C%20from%20electronic%20warfare%20to%20data%20links%20and%20cybersecurity%2C%20without%20relying%20on%20US-directed%20software%20update%20cycles.%20Those%20unique%20features%2C%20which%20allow%20the%20jet%20to%20be%20more%20tailored%20to%20Israeli%20needs%2C%20exclude%20it%20from%20US-provided%20updates%20for%20other%20F-35%20customers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIsraeli%20attacks%20on%20Iran%20have%20put%20the%20jet%20and%20the%20larger%20Israeli%20Air%20Force%20to%20the%20test.%20In%20the%20latest%20strikes%2C%20Israeli%20fighter%20jets%20struck%20over%20100%20targets%20across%20Iran%2C%20including%20key%20military%20sites%20and%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fimages-show-damage-iran-nuclear-fa