igure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22n%20this%20Sept.%2017%2C%202019%2C%20file%20photo%2C%20R.%20Kelly%20appears%20during%20a%20hearing%20at%20the%20Leighton%20Criminal%20Courthouse%20in%20Chicago.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F62815a2be7446d0018cc9376%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ER.%20Kelly%20remains%20behind%20bars%20at%20a%20North%20Carolina%20prison.%3Cp%3E(Antonio%20Perez%2FChicago%20Tribune%20via%20AP%2C%20Pool%2C%20File)%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3ER.%20Kelly's%20lawyer%20claims%20prison%20officials%20have%20a%20plot%20to%20kill%20the%20disgraced%20R%26amp%3BB%20singer.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20singer%20is%20seeking%20the%20%26quot%3Bintervention%26quot%3B%20of%20President%20Donald%20Trump%2C%20the%20attorney%20said.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EProsecutors%20call%20Kelly%20a%20%26quot%3Bprolific%20child%20molester%26quot%3B%20and%20his%20accusations%20a%20%26quot%3Bfanciful%20conspiracy.%26quot%3B%20%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EConvicted%20sex%20trafficker%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fr-kelly-victims-describe-abuse-by-his-fans-at-sentencing-2022-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ER.%20Kelly%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20hoping%20for%20President%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdonald-trump%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EDonald%20Trump's%3C%2Fa%3E%20help%2C%20said%20his%20lawyer%2C%20who%20has%20alleged%20that%20federal%20prison%20officials%20have%20devised%20a%20plot%20to%20kill%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fr-kelly-verdict-sex-crimes-chicago-trial-2022-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Edisgraced%20R%26amp%3BB%20singer%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20prison.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBureau%20of%20Prisons%20officers%20and%20officials%20are%20actively%20taking%20actions%20to%20kill%20R.%20Kelly%2C%26quot%3B%20Kelly's%20Chicago-based%20attorney%2C%20Beau%20Brindley%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider%20in%20a%20statement%20on%20Tuesday.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20asked%20for%20any%20evidence%20of%20the%20alleged%20murder%20plot%2C%20Brindley's%20law%20firm%20pointed%20BI%20to%20previously%20filed%20court%20documents.%20Federal%20prosecutors%20have%20called%20the%20accusations%20a%20%26quot%3Bfanciful%20conspiracy%26quot%3B%20in%20court%20papers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EKelly%20is%20serving%20a%2030-year%20sentence%20for%20sex%20trafficking%20and%20conspiracy.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20is%20now%20undeniable.%20And%2C%20it%20is%20because%20of%20this%20growing%20and%20imminent%20threat%20that%20we%20continue%20to%20seek%20the%20intervention%20of%20President%20Trump%2C%26quot%3B%20Brindley%20said%20in%20a%20written%20statement.%20%26quot%3BHe%20may%20be%20the%20only%20power%20in%20this%20country%20that%20can%20save%20a%20life%20and%20end%20this%20corruption%20before%20its%20too%20late.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EProsecutors%2C%20in%20court%20filings%20of%20their%20own%2C%20responded%20to%20Kelly's%20accusations%20made%20in%20a%20recent%20motion%2C%20saying%3A%20%26quot%3BThis%20is%20the%20behavior%20of%20an%20abuser%20and%20a%20master%20manipulator%20on%20display.%20Kelly%20is%20always%20the%20victim.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20White%20House%20did%20not%20immediately%20respond%20to%20a%20request%20for%20comment%20by%20Business%20Insider%20about%20whether%20Kelly's%20camp%20has%20reached%20out%20or%20whether%20Trump%20would%20ever%20consider%20a%20pardon%20for%20Kelly.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBrindley%20alleged%20in%20court%20filings%20this%20week%20that%20the%20incarcerated%20%26quot%3BIgnition%26quot%3B%20singer%20was%20rushed%20to%20a%20North%20Carolina%20hospital%20after%20officials%20at%20a%20prison%20in%20the%20state%20intentionally%20gave%20Kelly%20an%20%26quot%3Boverdose%26quot%3B%20of%20his%20medication.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EKelly%2C%20given%20name%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fthe-government-seized-27828-from-r-