20medication%20that%20significantly%20exceeded%20a%20safe%20dose%20and%20caused%20Mr.%20Kelly%20to%20overdose%2C%20putting%20his%20life%20in%20jeopardy.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey%20gave%20him%20an%20amount%20of%20medicine%20that%20could%20have%20killed%20him%2C%26quot%3B%20Brindley%20wrote%20in%20the%20court%20documents%2C%20which%20said%20Kelly%20takes%20medication%20for%20anxiety%20and%20to%20help%20him%20sleep%2C%20in%20addition%20to%20other%20medications.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EKelly%20awoke%20on%20Friday%20feeling%20%26quot%3Bfaint%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3Bdizzy%2C%26quot%3B%20Brindley%20wrote%20in%20the%20court%20papers%2C%20adding%20that%20Kelly%20%26quot%3Btried%20to%20get%20up%2C%20but%20fell%20to%20the%20ground%26quot%3B%20and%20later%20lost%20consciousness.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBrindley%20wrote%20that%20while%20at%20the%20hospital%2C%20blood%20clots%20were%20discovered%20in%20Kelly's%20legs%20and%20lungs%2C%20and%20that%20Kelly%20was%20told%20he%20would%20need%20surgery.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWithin%20an%20hour%2C%20officers%20with%20guns%20came%20into%20his%20hospital%20room%20and%20removed%20Mr.%20Kelly.%20He%20was%20taken%20from%20the%20hospital%20against%20his%20will%20and%20against%20the%20directives%20of%20the%20doctors%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20court%20filing%20says.%20%26quot%3BHe%20was%20denied%20the%20surgery%20he%20needs%20to%20clear%20blood%20clots%20in%20his%20lungs%20that%20threaten%20his%20life.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20another%20filing%20this%20week%2C%20Brindley%20wrote%2C%20%26quot%3BThese%20are%20outright%20acts%20by%20prison%20officials%20to%20put%20in%20jeopardy%20the%20life%20of%20a%20man%20who%20has%20endeavored%20to%20expose%20crimes%20committed%20by%20these%20officials%20themselves.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBrindley%20represented%20Kelly's%20former%20business%20manager%20in%20the%20singer's%20federal%20sex%20crimes%20trial%20in%20Chicago.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20case%20was%20tried%20in%20front%20of%20the%20same%20federa