a.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F06%2FIMG_7184_13b2f4d3-45b2-46e3-b884-5151d11a5b90_2873x_11zon-1750176144-1200x910.webp%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F06%2FIMG_7184_13b2f4d3-45b2-46e3-b884-5151d11a5b90_2873x_11zon-1750176144-150x114.webp%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-451095%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22379%5C%22%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-media-text__content%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20was%20determined%20to%20build%20a%20line%20of%20products%20that%20could%20offer%20long-term%20health%20benefits%20while%20addressing%20the%20deeper%20causes%20of%20ailments%20like%20PCOS.%20With%20the%20support%20of%20her%20husband%2C%20Soorya%2C%20who%20was%20working%20in%20the%20Indian%20Navy%2C%20they%20set%20their%20sights%20on%20creating%20a%20business%20that%20combined%20their%20passion%20for%20natural%20wellness%20with%20the%20growing%20demand%20for%20clean%20and%20plant-based%20products.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20December%202019%2C%20after%20years%20of%20research%20and%20experimentation%2C%20Cosmix%20was%20born.%20%E2%80%9CWhen%20we%20first%20started%2C%20protein%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20even%20part%20of%20our%20product%20range%2C%20and%20today%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20our%20biggest%20seller%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Soorya.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20began%20with%20very%20pure%20remedies%20aimed%20at%20improving%20digestion%2C%20sleep%2C%20stress%2C%20immunity%2C%20and%20more.%20Our%20core%20idea%20was%20to%20make%20products%20using%20herbs%20that%20are%20already%20available%20in%20most%20kitchens%2C%20like%3Cem%3E%20jeera%3C%2Fem%3E%20(cumin)%2C%20ginger%2C%20and%20%3Cem%3Eashwagandha%20(Indian%20Ginseng)%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20which%20are%20known%20for%20their%20specific%20health%20benefits.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVibha%20adds%2C%20%E2%80%9CWe%20didn%E2%80%99t%20want%20to%20complicate%20things.%20We%20focused%20on%20extracting%20and%20formulating%20these%20everyday%20ingredients%20in%20a%20way%20that%20would%20deliver%20the%20highest%20potency%20and%20best%20results%20for%20our%20customers.%20The%20uniqueness%20of%20our%20products%20was%20that%20we%20didn%E2%80%99t%20use%20any%20emulsifiers%20or%20bulking%20agents%20to%20make%20them%20taste%20better.%20We%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F246382%2Fdelhi-mother-daughter-startup-fight-domestic-violence-empower-women-organic-spices-buy-online-home-business-india-gop94%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewanted%20to%20offer%20raw%20ingredients%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20would%20directly%20support%20people%E2%80%99s%20health%20concerns.%20Of%20course%2C%20these%20products%20weren%E2%80%99t%20exactly%20tasty%20in%20the%20beginning%2C%20but%20people%20understood%20that%20they%20were%20making%20a%20health-conscious%20choice%2C%20and%20that%E2%80%99s%20when%20our%20business%20started%20to%20gain%20momentum.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%3Cins%20data-ad-slot%3D%5C%227521127830%5C%22%20data-ad-client%3D%5C%22ca-pub-5691287967087057%5C%22%20data-ad-format%3D%5C%22fluid%5C%22%20data-ad-layout%3D%5C%22in-article%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDr%20Ramakiran%2C%20Bachelor%20of%20Ayurvedic%20Medicine%20and%20Surgery%2C%20Doctor%20of%20Medicine%20(Ayurveda)%2C%20Post%20Graduate%20Certificate%20in%20Kidney%20Sciences%2C%20states%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20plant-based%20protein%20supplements%20contain%20no%20unnecessary%20additives%2C%20and%20what%20sets%20them%20apart%20is%20the%20carefully%20crafted%20herbal%20blend.%20This%20formulation%2C%20developed%20by%20a%20team%20of%20experts%2C%20is%20specifically%20designed%20to%20support%20digestion.%20Each%20batch%20also%20goes%20through%20lab%20testing%20to%20ensure%20safety%20and%20potency.%20The%20combination%20of%20high-quality%20ingredients%20and%20scientific%20expertise%20makes%20this%20protein%20not%20just%20effective%20but%20also%20a%20safe%20option.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDr%20Nidhi%20Tripathi%2C%20a%20gynaecologist%20and%20fertility%20specialist%20in%20Noida%2C%20with%20over%2012%20years%20of%20experience%2C%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CPCOS%20is%20a%20multifactorial%20disorder%20that%20affects%20our%20metabolism%20and%20can%20cause%20diabetes%2C%20obesity%2C%20and%20other%20health%20problems.%20While%20PCOS%20itself%20does%20not%20directly%20cause%20inflammation%2C%20it%20causes%20obesity%2C%20and%20this%20is%20what%20leads%20to%20inflammation%20in%20the%20body.%E2%80%9D%20She%20recommends%20incorporating%20anti-inflammatory%20foods%20like%20herbal%20blends%20such%20as%20ginger%2C%20turmeric%2C%20and%20fenugreek%20to%20help%20manage%20symptoms.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20also%20observes%20that%20many%20patients%20are%20shifting%20to%20plant-based%20protein%20due%20to%20its%20benefits%20in%20managing%20cholesterol.%20%E2%80%9CI%20have%20seen%20many%20patients%20switching%20to%20plant-based%20protein%20and%20now%2C%20they%20feel%20healthier%20and%20robust%2C%20and%20their%20cholesterol%20levels%20are%20also%20controlled%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%20She%20adds%2C%20%E2%80%9CWhile%20more%20studies%20are%20needed%20to%20prove%20this%2C%20it%20is%20the%20experiences%20of%20people%20that%20help%20to%20understand%20that%20this%20can%20be%20helpful.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%3Cins%20data-ad-slot%3D%5C%229669016977%5C%22%20data-ad-client%3D%5C%22ca-pub-5691287967087057%5C%22%20data-ad-format%3D%5C%22fluid%5C%22%20data-ad-layout%3D%5C%22in-article%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F06%2FBlue-and-Yellow-Modern-Business-Workshop-Facebook-Ad-2025-06-17T203517.232_11zon-1750172728.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Cosmix%20uses%20real%20ingredients%20such%20as%20vanilla%2