terindia.com%2F441112%2Fpushpa-prakash-68-year-old-trekker-bengaluru-everest-adventure%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ereach%20Everest%20Base%20Camp%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20a%20cycle%20but%20to%20start%20conversations%20about%20mental%20resilience%2C%20outdoor%20fitness%2C%20and%20personal%20growth%20through%20discomfort.%20%E2%80%9CI%20wanted%20to%20set%20an%20example%2C%20not%20as%20someone%20special%2C%20but%20as%20someone%20ordinary%20doing%20something%20unusual.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%3Cins%20data-ad-slot%3D%5C%227521127830%5C%22%20data-ad-client%3D%5C%22ca-pub-5691287967087057%5C%22%20data-ad-format%3D%5C%22fluid%5C%22%20data-ad-layout%3D%5C%22in-article%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECycling%20also%20unlocks%20a%20rare%20sense%20of%20freedom.%20With%20every%20push%20of%20the%20pedal%2C%20the%20mind%20begins%20to%20untangle%20itself%20from%20clutter%2C%20anxiety%2C%20or%20fear.%20The%20fresh%20air%2C%20the%20changing%20landscapes%2C%20the%20awareness%20of%20your%20breath%20and%20heartbeat%20%E2%80%94%20all%20of%20it%20grounds%20you%20in%20the%20present.%20For%20someone%20like%20Jyotishko%2C%20whose%20journeys%20often%20stretch%20over%20days%20and%20cross%20borders%2C%20the%20cycle%20becomes%20more%20than%20a%20machine%20%E2%80%94%20it%E2%80%99s%20a%20bridge%20between%20physical%20wellbeing%20and%20emotional%20strength.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EThe%20community%20that%20followed%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThough%20the%20ride%20was%20mostly%20solo%2C%20Jyotishko%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20alone%20in%20spirit.%20Over%20the%20years%2C%20he%E2%80%99s%20built%20strong%20connections%20in%20trekking%20and%20cycling%20communities%20across%20India%20and%20Nepal.%20While%20they%20didn%E2%80%99t%20fund%20his%20journey%2C%20many%20cheered%20him%20on%20and%20helped%20with%20logistics%20and%20morale.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOriginally%20from%20Arunachal%20Pradesh%2C%20Jyotishko%20has%20been%20living%20in%20West%20Bengal%20for%20work.%20%E2%80%9CI%20have%20always%20stayed%20in%20touch%20with%20Sherpa%20friends%20in%20Nepal%2C%20local%20guides%2C%20and%20even%20helped%20a%20school%20in%20Monjo%20by%20sending%20some%20supplies%20from%20Kathmandu%20before%20beginning%20the%20final%20trek%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20recalls.%20%E2%80%9CSo%2C%20in%20a%20way%2C%20this%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20just%20my%20journey.%20It%20was%20about%20the%20people%20and%20the%20communities%20that%20make%20up%20the%20Himalayan%20belt%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%3Cins%20data-ad-slot%3D%5C%229669016977%5C%22%20data-ad-client%3D%5C%22ca-pub-5691287967087057%5C%22%20data-ad-format%3D%5C%22fluid%5C%22%20data-ad-layout%3D%5C%22in-article%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CFor%20most%20people%2C%20just%20reaching%20Mount%20Everest%20Base%20Camp%20is%20a%20once-in-a-lifetime%20achievement.%20Jyotishko%20didn%E2%80%99t%20just%20get%20there%20%E2%80%94%20he%20cycled%20from%20West%20Bengal%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Malay%20Mukherjee%2C%20a%20veteran%20adventurer%2C%20cyclist%2C%20and%20Everest%20climber.%20Having%20mentored%20and%20witnessed%20many%20mountaineers%20over%20his%2026-year%20career%2C%20Malay%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20hold%20back%20his%20admiration.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EPedals%2C%20patience%2C%20and%20preparation%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJyotishko%20started%20his%20journey%20on%209%20February%202024%20from%20Digha.%20The%20route%20spanned%20around%201%2C346%20kilometres%2C%20cutting%20through%20West%20Bengal%2C%20into%20Nepal%20through%20Kakarbhitta%2C%20and%20finally%20to%20Everest%20Base%20Camp%20via%20Itahari%2C%20Okhaldhunga%2C%20Salleri%2C%20Namche%20Bazaar%2C%20and%20Gorakshep.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2